BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 208.8 750 Td (IEP BASICS EXPLAINED SIMPLY) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 738 m 552 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (WHAT IS AN IEP?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td (An Individualized Education Program \(IEP\) is a legal document that) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td (outlines the special education services your child will receive.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (WHO QUALIFIES?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (Children ages 3-21 with a disability that affects their ability) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (to learn in a general education setting. Must meet criteria under) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (one of 13 disability categories in IDEA \(Individuals with) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td (Disabilities Education Act\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (WHAT DOES AN IEP INCLUDE?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (- Present levels of performance \(where your child is NOW\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (- Annual goals \(what they'll work toward this year\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (- Special education services \(speech, OT, resource room, etc.\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td (- Accommodations and modifications) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (- How progress will be measured and reported) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (- Transition planning \(age 14-16, depending on state\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td (WHO IS ON THE IEP TEAM?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td (- YOU \(the parent - the MOST important member!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (- General education teacher) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (- Special education teacher) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td (- School administrator \(LEA representative\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td (- Related service providers \(as applicable\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td (- Your child \(when appropriate\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 315 Td (- Anyone else YOU invite \(advocate, family member, tutor\)) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
