BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 198.0 750 Td (YOUR RIGHTS AS A PARENT \(IDEA\)) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 738 m 552 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (Under the Individuals with Disabilities Education Act \(IDEA\),) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td (you have these LEGAL RIGHTS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (1. RIGHT TO PARTICIPATE in ALL decisions about your child) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (2. RIGHT TO INFORMED CONSENT before evaluations or placement changes) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (3. RIGHT TO ACCESS all educational records) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (4. RIGHT TO AN INDEPENDENT EDUCATIONAL EVALUATION \(IEE\) at) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (   district expense if you disagree with their evaluation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td (5. RIGHT TO WRITTEN NOTICE before any changes to services) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (6. RIGHT TO DISAGREE and use dispute resolution) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (7. RIGHT TO BRING ANYONE to IEP meetings \(advocate, attorney\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (8. RIGHT TO REQUEST an IEP meeting at any time) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (9. RIGHT TO A FREE APPROPRIATE PUBLIC EDUCATION \(FAPE\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (10. RIGHT TO LEAST RESTRICTIVE ENVIRONMENT \(LRE\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (IMPORTANT: Everything should be IN WRITING.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (Verbal promises mean nothing. If it's not in the IEP, it) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td (does not have to be provided.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td (TIPS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (- Always follow up conversations with a confirming email) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (- Keep a binder of ALL correspondence and documents) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td (- Record meetings if your state allows \(check state law\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td (- You can say 'I need time to think about this' at any meeting) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td (- You do NOT have to sign the IEP the same day) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
