BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 201.60000000000002 750 Td (ACCOMMODATION vs MODIFICATION) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 738 m 552 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (These are NOT the same thing. Know the difference!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 700 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 685 Td (ACCOMMODATION = Changes HOW a child learns) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 670 Td (\(same content, same expectations, different access\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 655 Td (Examples:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 640 Td (- Extended time on tests) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 625 Td (- Preferential seating) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 610 Td (- Text-to-speech technology) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 595 Td (- Fidget tools allowed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 580 Td (- Breaks between tasks) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 565 Td (- Reduced homework quantity \(same difficulty\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 550 Td (- Large print materials) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 535 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 520 Td (MODIFICATION = Changes WHAT a child learns) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 505 Td (\(different content or lower expectations\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 490 Td (Examples:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (- Simplified assignments) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 460 Td (- Alternate grading criteria) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 445 Td (- Different curriculum entirely) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 430 Td (- Fewer answer choices on tests) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 415 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 400 Td (WHY IT MATTERS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 385 Td (Accommodations do NOT affect grade-level diploma eligibility.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 370 Td (Modifications MAY affect diploma type in some states.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 355 Td (Always push for accommodations FIRST.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 340 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 325 Td (MY CHILD'S ACCOMMODATIONS I'M REQUESTING:) Tj ET
