q 0 G 1 w 60 738 m 552 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (If you disagree with the school's decisions, you have options:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td (STEP 1: Put your concerns IN WRITING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (Send a letter/email stating specifically what you disagree with) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (and what you want instead. Keep it factual and professional.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (STEP 2: Request another IEP meeting) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (You can request a meeting at any time to discuss concerns.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (STEP 3: Facilitated IEP meeting) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (Request a neutral facilitator to guide the discussion.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (STEP 4: Mediation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (Free, voluntary process with a trained mediator.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td (Both sides must agree to participate. Faster than due process.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (STEP 5: State Complaint) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td (File with your state education department. They investigate) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td (whether the school violated IDEA. Decision within 60 days.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (STEP 6: Due Process Hearing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (Formal legal hearing before an impartial hearing officer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td (Consider hiring a special education attorney for this step.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td (REMEMBER:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 315 Td (- Document EVERYTHING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 299 Td (- Stay calm and professional \(it's hard but essential\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 283 Td (- Focus on your child's NEEDS, not blame) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 267 Td (- Get support: parent training centers, advocates) Tj ET

endstream
